node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Uloo - Stay Curious! on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Career & Skills Mindful Journey to Inclusiveness with Laurence 20-24 September, 2021'.

node.text:
Join us to work on our Career & Skills with this new Uloo Team Challenge: Mindful Journey to Inclusiveness.⠀
⠀
In this challenge, you will learn to become more familiar with the most common unconscious biases and become more mindful of your own reactions. It will encourage you to understand further - and to reprogram - your unconscious beliefs. At work, these are important leadership skills for collaborating, innovating, recruiting, retaining talents more effectively; for becoming an active advocate of inclusiveness, and build a more vibrant workplace. ⠀
⠀
Join this Team Challenge if you:⠀
-> Want to embody better the value of inclusiveness in the workplace⠀
-> Are willing to become more mindful of our common unconscious biases⠀
-> Are ready to transform yourself.⠀
⠀
This Team Challenge starts 20 September, with the Kick-Off virtual meeting at 7 pm (CET) | 1 pm (ET) | 10.30 pm (IST). Secure your spot by joining the Team Challenge now and see you at the Kick-Off!⠀
⠀
More Info & Join 👉 https://uloo.me/team-challenges/mindful-journey-to-inclusiveness-with-laurence
⠀
Kick-Off Link 👉 https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85705052996?pwd=RDVLSGZyYWZscTFiOXlLcjRMZzZzdz09
(Passcode: uloo)⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Uloo - Stay Curious! on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting, indoor and text that says ':ะะ International Literacy Day'.

node.text:
Today we're celebrating International Literacy Day! 📚⠀
Initiated by UNESCO in 1967, this celebration reminds us of the importance of literacy as a matter of dignity and human rights and advances the agenda of a literate and sustainable society.⠀
⠀
How can we celebrate International Literacy Day?⠀
📖  Donate books to local library or classroom⠀
🎁  Gift a book to children, motivate their curiosity to read⠀
🤝  Start or participate in a lending community. A free community library with the concept of "take a book, return a book" will help books be more accessible to everyone.⠀
⠀
And to celebrate with us, why not join our book club?⠀
Stay tuned for our next book club Team Challenge!⠀
⠀
#InternationalLiteracyDay #LiteracyDay #UNESCO #reading #book #books
